::Hot Rod::

He suddenly felt like he had to be somewhere els.
"Vehical mode." 
He transformed to car mode, and drove off. At first he didn't know where
he was going, but he checked his course eventualy.
He was headed for what would be.... Autobot City.

::Dollen::

He opened a comm to the traders.
"Hello..? Anyone home? I have brought the goods."

::Demolition::

He opened a comm to Havoc.
"Hey boss, where are you?"
